Name
    File::MealMaster - OO access to the MealMaster recipe files

Version
    This documents version v0.18.$Rev: 1 $ of File::MealMaster

Synopsis
       use File::MealMaster;

       my $mealmaster_ref = File::MealMaster->new( $mealmaster_attributes );

Description
    Extends File::DataClass::Schema. Defines the "recipes" result source

Configuration and Environment
    Defines these attributes:

    "cache_attributes"
    "cache_class"
    "result_source_attributes"
    "source_name"
       Defaults to "recipes". The result source name in the schema
       definition

    Modifies these methods;

    "resultset"
    "source"

Subroutines/Methods
  make_key
    Exposes make_key

Diagnostics
    None

Dependencies
    File::DataClass::Schema
    File::MealMaster::Result
    File::MealMaster::Storage
    Moo

Incompatibilities
    There are no known incompatibilities in this module

Bugs and Limitations
    There are no known bugs in this module. Please report problems to the
    address below. Patches are welcome

Author
    Peter Flanigan, "<pjfl@cpan.org>"

